| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3546 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 93d01b4c-bc74-5ec5-9f4a-87a1ba45f614"
